## Quick Token Reference

Colors:     ui/Color.kt, presentation/common/OfferLashColors.kt
Spacing:    ui/Spacing.kt
Dimensions: ui/Dimens.kt
Typography: ui/Type.kt, ui/Font.kt
Shapes:     ui/Shapes.kt
Theme:      ui/Theme.kt

## When Making Changes

1. Check app tokens first
2. Use existing tokens when possible
3. If new token needed, add to app first
4. Propagate to web after approval
5. Document the change

